          "id": "36959129c7a7a32c6c785c39c9dc4e828448f044",
          "message": "test: increase core coverage to 87% + codecov config (#10)\n\n* fix: add codecov config and update README title\n\n- Ignore examples/, bench/, cmd/ from coverage reports\n- Set patch coverage target to 80%\n- Update tagline: Fast by default, type-safe by design\n- Remove Thai text from title\n\n* test: increase core coverage from 60% to 87%\n\nAdd comprehensive tests for previously uncovered code paths:\n- ctx_fasthttp_test.go: fasthttp context adapter, ServeFast lifecycle\n- nethttp_adapter_test.go: net/http request/response adapters\n- config_wing_test.go: Wing transport config and env vars\n- coverage_boost_test.go: static serving, views, app methods, context\n\n* test: fix empty branch lint warnings (SA9003)\n\n* test: push core coverage from 87% to 90%+\n\nAdd tests for config options, DI container, context methods,\ngroup routing, health checks, JSON encoding, and validation.\njson package: 28% → 100%.\n\n* test: fix lint SA1029 and Windows timer flake in latency test\n\n* test: add coverage for resource, router, devmode, and kruda edge cases\n\n* test: fix SA9003 empty branch in coverage_boost3",
